Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:25.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この先に何かいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:25.41,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,There's something past here... {Thought}
