Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:36.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）こ… こら 貴様！\N先導車を抜くな！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:36.63,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't go in front of the guide chariot!
